title: VA slow motion (blue tunes records)
description:
VA slow motion (blue tunes records)

The first release in 2008 is a colourful and trippy 
chill out and lounge collection with magical and unique ambient tunes.
Some known artists of Blue Tunes show us another side with fresh and hypnotic
atmospheres. This journey will be one-of-a-kind and overwhelming with warm 
and soft beats. A start with finest motion.
